---
import ToolLayout from "../layouts/ToolLayout.astro";

const title = "Privacy Policy";
const description =
  "Privacy Policy for Easy2GoHub. Learn how we handle data, cookies, and third-party advertising (Google AdSense).";
const canonical = "https://www.easy2gohub.com/privacy-policy/";
---

<ToolLayout title={title} description={description} canonical={canonical} adsProfile="none">
  <section class="tool-card p-10 space-y-6">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-slate-900">Privacy Policy</h2>
    <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
      This Privacy Policy describes how Easy2GoHub (“we”, “our”, “us”) collects, uses, and shares information when you
      use our website and tools.
    </p>

    <div class="space-y-3">
      <h3 class="text-xl font-extrabold text-slate-900">1) Local Processing</h3>
      <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
        Our tools are designed to run locally in your browser whenever possible. Files you process (such as images or PDFs)
        are not uploaded to our servers unless a feature explicitly states otherwise.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="space-y-3">
      <h3 class="text-xl font-extrabold text-slate-900">2) Analytics & Log Data</h3>
      <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
        Like most websites, we may collect basic usage data (for example, pages visited, browser type, and approximate
        region) to improve performance and user experience. This data is used in aggregate and does not directly identify you.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="space-y-3">
      <h3 class="text-xl font-extrabold text-slate-900">3) Cookies</h3>
      <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
        We and our partners may use cookies or similar technologies to deliver and measure ads and to understand site usage.
        You can control cookies through your browser settings.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="space-y-3">
      <h3 class="text-xl font-extrabold text-slate-900">4) Google AdSense</h3>
      <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
        We may display advertisements served by Google AdSense. Google may use cookies to serve ads based on your visits to
        this and other websites. You can opt out of personalized advertising by visiting Google’s Ads Settings.
      </p>
      <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
        Learn more about how Google uses information from sites or apps that use its services in Google’s policies.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="space-y-3">
      <h3 class="text-xl font-extrabold text-slate-900">5) Data Security</h3>
      <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
        We take reasonable steps to protect the website. However, no method of transmission over the internet or method of
        electronic storage is 100% secure.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="space-y-3">
      <h3 class="text-xl font-extrabold text-slate-900">6) Changes</h3>
      <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
        We may update this policy from time to time. The updated version will be posted on this page.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="space-y-3">
      <h3 class="text-xl font-extrabold text-slate-900">7) Contact</h3>
      <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
        If you have questions about this policy, you can contact us at:
        <span class="font-semibold"> easy2gohub@gmail.com</span>
      </p>
      <p class="text-xs text-slate-400 font-semibold">
        Last updated: 2026-02-11
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</ToolLayout>
